{"tid":1394710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大量單車頭盔呀！埋嚟睇埋嚟揀喇喂！","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:07:30.000Z","uid":282709,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9510cccc2124e7f7e49b27567b686859ee1edf70","tid":1394710,"uid":282709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:37:32.000Z","msg":"《P牌首貼請多多指教》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近好多人踩單車，聽聞好難買頭盔，上網見到以下2款頭盔，唔知啱唔啱用？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ckwuPpy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FckwuPpy.png&h=14aa2a25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySHmFwe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySHmFwe.png&h=ea18c669&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTugupz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTugupz.png&h=8d5a50b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWkSNbf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWkSNbf.png&h=6d978245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩款頭盔入面都有發泡膠墊。<br />\n<br />\n唔知第2款會唔會太細？<br />\n<br />\n澳洲網購，海關唔會扣貨掛？<br />\n<br />\n郵費唔平，但如果啱駛，我試下入少少貨帶出去俾同路人試用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86a1ffdcb13704ea4ea2717b1c93097f478b04f","tid":1394710,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8742d59cf7bf10387a21d228172c8e91c65947e8","tid":1394710,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:40:12.000Z","msg":"第一款係咪有洞？有洞唔好"},{"pid":"2f6a1f8824c2f32455c6617999cb69ac81e8a1d8","tid":1394710,"uid":282709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8742d59cf7bf10387a21d228172c8e91c65947e8","tid":1394710,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislik